- **Tech-specific rules**: Use specific glob patterns to avoid conflicts
- **Keep rules under 500 lines**: Split large rules into composable files
- **Provide concrete examples**: Reference actual code when possible
- **Clear rule hierarchy**: Manual > Auto Attached > Always > Agent Requested

